			>
			<P>I thought about something like this in another post here this was my take on it:</P>
<P>someone said about how to let us be better at off tanking, here wa my idea on another thread,</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<DIV>
<DIV>I for one would love to bring back the Ghetto crowd control again. what about if they made a new spell like our AA mini earth elementals?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>what I mean is we have little mini earth elemenatls we can summon up to assist our pet in battle for a short time. why not make a new&nbsp; mini horde that are air pets and you could send it on a target that would&nbsp;perma stun the mob&nbsp;for a fixed duration&nbsp;but it wont do any damage to the mob. with the mob being stunned he wont be hitting the horde and he would be "offtanked/parked".</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;the stun would be broken once the mob took damage, like someone breaking mezz.&nbsp; mages ask for root/snare this could be one way of adding it in.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>also this would be a form of a spell not an AA like my original idea, this way more levels could use it. we could get this spell at 40 and it would last 3 mins. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>this would "fit in" with us useing elementals to help us, the air pet is know to stun mobs that no other class can so why wouldn't it make sense of us useing&nbsp; "mini air elementals"&nbsp;as well?&nbsp;wouldn't we have learned to use other elemental hordes by now? we have mastered the elements right?</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>yes this idea could use work but I feel if we can make it "fit" in lore with the class the better the chance at getting something done should improve</DIV></DIV>
<DIV></DIV>	
